Package com.g1.mychess.match.dto

Class MatchDTO

java.lang.Object
com.g1.mychess.match.dto.MatchDTO
public class MatchDTO extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) for representing match information in a tournament. This class is used to transfer match data between layers of the application.
